    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}The key ingredient is the Manganji pepper. Remember to remove the seeds first![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}After that, we'll prepare some kombu soup stock. You'll need a pasta cooker about this size, and...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
